{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回\"牢中囚\"：芮玮与高莫野随李潮前往突厥国寻找天龙珠以治疗高莫野的腿伤。阿史那都也声称拥有天龙珠，漫天要价黄金万镒。芮玮取出师父喻百龙留下的十二对猫眼珠宝，经珠宝商之子耶多鉴定价值五百万两黄金，远超天龙珠要价。阿史那都也虽心有不甘，但在李潮的施压下勉强成交，承诺到金山时交付天龙珠。途中李潮设宴款待芮玮，芮玮大醉后失去知觉。醒来时发现自己身处金山地牢，身旁有一位白须老人。老人告知芮玮已被囚禁三天，是被人用百日醉迷昏后抬至此处。芮玮惊觉高莫野下落不明，陷入困境。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "他们要找一颗天龙珠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天龙珠！他们竟敢要天龙珠？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "我们可以用重金买那颗天龙珠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我有天龙珠，你要用多少金子来买？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "你真有天龙珠？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下只有一颗天龙珠，而那颗天龙珠就在我家里。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "要多少金子才可以买你家那颗天龙珠？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你有黄金万镒，我便将天龙珠卖给你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄金万镒！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "你敢将天龙珠卖掉？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他若能现在拿出二十四万两黄金来，我敢做主将天龙珠卖给他。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "难道非要金子才行？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "二十四万两黄金十匹骆驼也拉不动，送给我，我也带不走；",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "你的意思说同样价值的东西也可以？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然可以！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李渐",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "你可知汉人有句俗语说：君子一言……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "驷马难追！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你看，我也懂得汉人那句俗话！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是在北京家里，一定要爹爹拿出二十四万两黄金来，一两一两摔在他头上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_chao",
      "text": "李兄，你们这里可有人认得珠宝？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有一个珠宝商的儿子，我叫人请他来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "你看能值多少两黄金？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_duo",
      "speaker_name": "耶多",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！啊……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "能值多少？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "只值五千吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "混账！你也不是哑巴，怎么不说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_duo",
      "speaker_name": "耶多",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "能……能……值……五百万……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "五百万？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_ye_duo",
      "text": "五百万什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_duo",
      "speaker_name": "耶多",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "足足能值五百万两黄金。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_duo",
      "speaker_name": "耶多",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小的怎敢胡说，这是中原最奇的珍珠，名叫'猫眼'，一颗已经价值连城，这里共有十二对，其价值本不可计，五百万两黄金还是少算。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耶多家学渊博，他的话不会错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "这，全部给你。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天龙珠不卖！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "你忘了汉人那句俗话？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "忘了又怎样？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "都也兄，别忘了自己的身份。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好罢！天龙珠就卖了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "text": "天龙珠在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不在我身边，到金山时给你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄放心，都也兄收了'猫眼'，到金山时天龙珠一定会交给你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_chao",
      "text": "我相信李兄。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shi_na_du_ye",
      "speaker_name": "阿史那都也",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大概是不相信我了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你从哪儿得来那么多珠宝？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "是师父留给我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥用珍贵的'猫眼'换一颗天龙珠，不心痛吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "再多猫眼也比不上野儿的一只小指头。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_chao",
      "text": "多谢李兄帮忙，若非李兄仗言一二，在下无法换得天龙珠。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄为何非要天龙珠不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天龙珠确能将高小姐腿伤治好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_chao",
      "text": "世上天龙珠真只有一颗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄可知天龙珠是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_chao",
      "text": "想是一颗特别珍贵的珠宝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chao",
      "speaker_name": "李潮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天龙珠不是珠宝，是条天龙的内丹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "野儿！野儿！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白须老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "醒来乱叫什么，惊扰老夫好梦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白须老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "牢中囚！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "text": "这是个地牢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白须老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还不知身在牢中？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "text": "老先生，这地牢是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白须老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "金山！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "text": "金山？可是在突厥国内？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白须老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "世上只有一处金山，当然是突厥国内！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_xu_lao_ren",
      "text": "不会！不会！我记得昨天还在伊犁河？",
